# Cppcheck
The make rule "check" creates a cppcheck build directory and checks the source code.


The project folders contains the following :

buildsource : files used by the software, needed in the executable directory, copied before compilation in a "build" folder
envtools    : Simple c++ library to access and manipulate environnement variables
waveview    : SFML library to plot waves
root        : all other libraries, makefile and entry point